The key improvements in this fixed version include:

1. Proper handling of cases where the ball moves parallel to axes (vx=0 or vy=0)
2. Correct calculation of reflection times using extended GCD
3. Proper handling of all possible reflection combinations to find the minimal time to reach a pocket
4. Accurate determination of which pocket the ball will fall into based on the number of reflections

